## Adding Data Quality to Observation Space

Including data quality as an observation feature allows the RL agent to learn context-dependent behavior based on data source reliability.

```python
import numpy as np
from gymnasium import spaces

observation_space = spaces.Dict({
    # ... existing features ...
    "data_quality": spaces.Box(
        low=0.0, high=1.0, shape=(1,), dtype=np.float32
    ),
    "using_fallback": spaces.Discrete(2),
})
```

